title: 313. Q&AF: Visualizing Long Term Goals, Voting Out Established Politicians & Leadership Through Inspiration

description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on why you should take visualization of your long-term goals seriously, how you can get involved in your community to vote out established politicians, and why leading by example is the most effective way to lead your team.
